NYSE Board Reaffirms Commitment to Combination With Deutsche Boerse AG

-- B y   D a n   H a r t
-- 
2011-04-10T17:25:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-10/nyse-board-reaffirms-commitment-to-combination-with-deutsche-boerse-ag.html
The  NYSE Euronext (NYX)  board said it has
“unanimously reaffirmed” the planned agreement by  Deutsche
Boerse AG (DB1)  to buy the exchange.  The e-mailed statement was made after a meeting of the
board, which rejected a competing bid from  Nasdaq OMX Group Inc. (NDAQ)   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Hart at 
 dahart@bloomberg.net  